//- inlookup.jade is a nested view for a ui-grid lookup table.
    It includes a grid, pagination controls, and a nested table for editing.
    This view only shows when the page is in the in.inlookup state.
    The in parent view with a search field is always showing with this
div(ng-show='vm.show')
  h3
    br
    | Inventory Lookup Table&nbsp
  p Select a row to edit
  .myGrid(ui-grid='vm.gridOptions', ui-grid-selection, ui-grid-pagination)
  button.btn.btn-default(type='button', ng-click='vm.gridApi.pagination.previousPage()')
    span.fa.fa-arrow-left
  span  Page: {{vm.gridApi.pagination.getPage()}}
  span / {{vm.gridApi.pagination.getTotalPages()}} 
  button.btn.btn-default(type='button', ng-click='vm.gridApi.pagination.nextPage()')
    span.fa.fa-arrow-right
div(ui-view='')